PN,40301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778854268
OL,3,CBlood test could determine if prostate
OL,4,Ccancer treatment is failing
OL,6,FA new blood test could help doctors
OL,7,Fpinpoint at an earlier stage if a
OL,8,Fman's prostate cancer treatment is
OL,9,Ffailing, a trial has found.
OL,11,FThe discovery could lead to
OL,12,Fpersonalised treatments for the
OL,13,Fdisease, experts said, as well as
OL,14,Fhelping patients with advanced cancer
OL,15,Fto live longer.
OL,17,FThe study, led by University College
OL,18,FLondon, explored if tests looking at
OL,19,Ftiny fragments of tumour DNA in the
OL,20,Fblood could determine if cancer was
OL,21,Fstill growing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
