FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778854268
OL,3,CBlood test could determine if prostate
OL,4,Ccancer treatment is failing
OL,6,FIt included 117 men across 14 NHS
OL,7,Fsites with newly diagnosed metastatic
OL,8,Fprostate cancer, meaning it had spread
OL,9,Felsewhere in the body.
OL,11,FResearchers found three in 10 men had
OL,12,Fdetectable levels of tumour DNA in
OL,13,Ftheir blood after six to 12 weeks of
OL,14,Ftreatment.
OL,16,FWhen combined, blood tests that looked
OL,17,Fat tumour DNA and prostate specific
OL,18,Fantigen (PSA) levels identified men
OL,19,Fwho were 20 times more likely to die
OL,20,Fcompared to those with undetectable
OL,21,Ftumour DNA and low PSA levels.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778854268
OL,3,CBlood test could determine if prostate
OL,4,Ccancer treatment is failing
OL,6,FProfessor Gerhardt Attard, who led the
OL,7,Fstudy at University College London,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is so exciting because
OL,9,Fit's the first time we've ever seen
OL,10,Fsuch a clear link between tumour DNA
OL,11,Fin the blood and outcomes for men with
OL,12,Fhormone-sensitive advanced cancer.
OL,14,F"By using it alongside PSA blood
OL,15,Ftests, we can personalise treatments
OL,16,Fand help find the right balance
OL,17,Fbetween reducing side effects and
OL,18,Fgiving men more time with their loved
OL,19,Fones.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
