OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778854268
OL,3,CBlood test could determine if prostate
OL,4,Ccancer treatment is failing
OL,6,F"The next step is to show that we can
OL,7,Freproduce this and how it can be used
OL,8,Fin practice. That's why we're
OL,9,Fimplementing it across all our
OL,10,Fclinical trials for advanced prostate
OL,11,Fcancer to get the evidence we need to
OL,12,Froll this out as soon as possible."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
