FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778854268
OL,3,CBlood test could determine if prostate
OL,4,Ccancer treatment is failing
OL,6,FDr Hayley Luxton, head of research,
OL,7,Fimpact and engagement at Prostate
OL,8,FCancer UK, which funded the study
OL,9,Falongside Movember, said: "Thousands
OL,10,Fof men are diagnosed with advanced,
OL,11,Fincurable prostate cancer every year,
OL,12,Fand right now, we can't say which
OL,13,Ftreatment will be best for which man
OL,14,Funtil much later on.
OL,16,F"By showing if treatments are
OL,17,Feffective so much sooner, this test
OL,18,Fcould not only help men with advanced
OL,19,Fprostate cancer live longer and
OL,20,Fbetter, but could also massively speed
OL,21,Fup prostate cancer research in future."
OL,26,@qD@[OUxD@AOU}D@gO]
